-- Factbox: Gold milestones on the road to record high
-- 
-- Fri Jun 18, 2010 10:09am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/06/18/us-precious-milestones-idUSTRE65H2K920100618

 

 LONDON  (Reuters) - Gold hit record highs near $1,260 an ounce on Friday as investors bought the metal as a haven from sovereign risk and further financial market instability, with a weak dollar adding impetus to its rise. 

